{"tid":967392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳若希稱對肌肉男先有興趣　斗膽在老公Alex面前高呼：我單身㗎！","createTime":"2019-01-03T12:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T03:13:47.000Z","uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1851774e2c674de955614e6660d390549102a3","tid":967392,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"踏入2019年， 韓國男團2PM成員俊昊特地來香港和吳若希、李佳芯等藝人一同出席倒數派對。 吳若希去年和金鐘國在老公面前上演了鐵達尼號的戲碼， 今年同樣有韓星出席倒數活動，相信大家也十分關心吳若希會和俊昊有什麼互動。<br />\n<br />\n在活動上吳若希一上台就馬上借用了六號（陸浩明）的電話去和2PM成員俊昊自拍。自拍後，Jinny更在老公Alex面前大叫表示：<span style=\"color: green;\">「我冇結過婚！我單身㗎！」</span>其實在活動前，吳若希在接受《香港01》記者訪問時表示今年老公同樣在場，會收斂一些，更表示自己對肌肉男才有興趣，她更指：「今晚的oppa走靚仔風格。」未知老公在台下望到有甚麽感受呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYvk4Lc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYvk4Lc.png&h=9346634f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tw5M0iz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftw5M0iz.png&h=2892d727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhjYRqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhjYRqf.png&h=b5c1b6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a2223ed706774dc9352858e132f9537867bd52e","tid":967392,"uid":146631,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6187776d63480a0a5792991eafc084b50f647dea","tid":967392,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"唔通何生沉咗船?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61464e6218820f333b1fbfaaa0a39b0c45e2af59","tid":967392,"uid":171107,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲女做舞小姐出身既騎功一定一流<